doing horror movies.

284
00:20:12,010 --> 00:20:15,411
He actually told me he hadn't
called in the last ten years...

285
00:20:15,447 --> 00:20:18,814
because he hadn't had
any really scary nightmares.

286
00:20:18,850 --> 00:20:21,614
